## What Caused the Delay?

Sources indicate that several logistical and administrative challenges may have contributed to the delay. These could include venue coordination, international tour schedules, and broadcasting agreements.

The Indian Premier League is one of the most watched cricket tournaments in the world, so even small scheduling changes can create major ripple effects.

## Impact on Teams and Fans

Teams usually begin planning months in advance, organizing training camps, travel arrangements, and player availability. A delayed schedule announcement makes preparation more difficult.

Fans are also eagerly waiting to plan travel and tickets, especially those hoping to attend matches in person.

